properties.name: The Gongbei Port
properties.description:
The Gongbei Port is an immigration and customs checkpoint within the People's Republic of China between the province of Guandong and the Special Administrative Region of Macau. It is located in the Gongbei neighborhood (jiedao) in the south-eastern part of Zhuhai City, Guangdong, and is one of two points of entry between the mainland and Macau (the other being the Lotus Bridge, connecting Cotai, Macau, with Hengqin, Zhuhai). As one faces toward the gate from Zhuhai, immigration and customs for travelers exiting mainland China are to the left, while immigration and customs for those entering mainland China are to right.
---- Wikipedia
